Tired Of Failing The Challenges?

We help you pass the Challenge phases within 5 days and take you to a live account. 90% of the prop firm challenge buyers do not go to live accounts. We help you with this short cut.

We use the special HFT software to pass phase 1 and phase 2. 100% guaranteed result.

GET 1 EA LICENSE FOR FREE FOR LIVE ACCOUNT

We provide you 1 license of Stellar EA or Elite EA for free on purchasing 100K or above account. You can use it on Live funded account or on your personal account

We accept only below mentioned prop firm challenges & MT4 only

Prop Firms we accept, MT4 Accounts only:
  • NextStepFunded (100% Success) – (Only 2 Step Challenge accepted)
  • Quantec Funding (100% Success) – (Only 2 Step Challenge accepted)
  • Infinity Forex Funds (100% Success) – (Only Algo Evaluation accepted)
  • Nova Funding (100% Success) – (All types accepted)
  • Social Trading Club (100% Success) – (Only One Step Challenge accepted)
VIEW PLANS

Myfxbook Track Record

View Myfxbook

Features

Short Cut To Live Funded Account

1. Purchase the account

According to your challenge account size purchase our plan

2. Send us MT4 Credentials

We do all the setup after you provide details and let you know

3. Profit target reached

Within 1 to 3 days you will see the profit target reached, simple!

Note: We do not manage Live Funded accounts. We just help you to pass the challenge.

Pricing

No Hidden Charges

You can pay only 50% first and after passing phase 1 you can pay remaining 50% to pass phase 2(Only applicable for 2 phase challenge). Use Coupon code HALF.

We accept only the above mentioned prop firms. Please read the list before buying.

Note: we do not provide EA in this service. You must provide MT4 credentials and we will pass the challenge. We do not work with MT5.
